• Each box contains 10 Theme Boosters: 2 each of the five bi-colored Ravnican Guilds booster packs:
- Azorius UW
- Gruul RG
- Orzhov BW
- Rakdos BR
- Simic UG

• Each Theme Booster has 35 random cards, with one guaranteed to be a mythic or rare, all in the colors of the Guild on the pack!
